{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"369d8dcdc5afea1052bcbce32d0f11fc110085d751bc3c33dd090fe44fe1be6e","slug":"2026-03-26","location":"/journal/qtclass/vip/2026-03-26.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"2026-03-26","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":3}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/journal/qtclass/vip/2026-03-26.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/journal/qtclass/vip/2026-03-26.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"2026-03-26.md","url":"/2026-03-26-24c316ec35562f31edbd4cc79b88be31.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"标题：Vibe Coding设计阶段\n主题：“文档驱动开发”和“测试驱动开发”在Vibe Coding时代的新含义。\n档案：docs/profile/qtclass/train/lecture2.md","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"BJ0ybBMhp0"}],"key":"Rxst5TcDwf"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Spec-Driven-> Plan Driven\nSpec-Driven: gujia","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"kI7oezIKmF"}],"key":"Eg89n0H7mO"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"spec + usercase\n-> add docs + context\n-> dev docs + ROADMAP\n-> plan\n-> user docs -> docs test","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"Zvnuv3NfSI"}],"key":"GhuVPKhHts"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"docs","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"N7BzhCZQVk"}],"key":"kEieY9eKU2"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何形成可用的文档？脱离屏幕。\n90%时间设计。","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"Tbco2DiEiV"}],"key":"OcIGCLly60"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开发者的认知水平","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"fLhFK5VCMa"}],"key":"Pylvlw5xcV"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前Vibe时代：没有认知水平=写不出代码\nVibe时代：没有也可以先写，但是效率更高。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"ElC9Uqr1oo"}],"key":"ojubrNLizw"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"-> Vibe Coding的设计是提高自己的认知水平\n为了更好地掌控代码（不变的目的）","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"I4B3KL5kem"}],"key":"Q2J2vATKv9"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"举例","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"v2iRbc6x6B"}],"identifier":"id","label":"举例","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"oWtS47JGN0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感觉：我的文章内部有关联，但是我自己看不到。\n相似度：质谱给我算相似度。生成了四种相似度。\nAI解读：不同的相似度有不同的含义\n->\n不同类型的相似度可以用来作为规则引擎得出关于文本关联的结论\n->\n文本联想引擎","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"YRe3N9IVTM"}],"key":"wAaNYk9wVC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"as 设计结果","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"x9JuSeNL33"}],"key":"EXYgsZLdM7"},{"type":"code","lang":"","value":"\n【1. Jaccard 相似度】\n原理: 两个文本词集合的交集大小 / 并集大小\n特点: 只关注词汇是否出现，不考虑频率和顺序\n适用: 快速判断文本是否共享很多相同词汇\n\n  article1 vs article2: 0.3261 (32.61%)\n  article1 vs article3: 0.2863 (28.63%)\n  article2 vs article3: 0.2832 (28.32%)\n\n【2. Dice 相似度】\n原理: 2 × 交集大小 / (集合A大小 + 集合B大小)\n特点: 与Jaccard类似，但更强调交集的影响\n适用: 词汇重合度的另一种衡量方式\n\n  article1 vs article2: 0.4918 (49.18%)\n  article1 vs article3: 0.4451 (44.51%)\n  article2 vs article3: 0.4414 (44.14%)\n\n【3. TF-IDF 余弦相似度】\n原理: 基于TF-IDF权重，计算向量夹角的余弦值\n特点: 考虑词频和词的重要性( IDF )\n适用: 比较文本主题相似性，常用于文档检索\n\n  article1 vs article2: 0.0899 (8.99%)\n  article1 vs article3: 0.0578 (5.78%)\n  article2 vs article3: 0.0289 (2.89%)\n\n【4. 编辑距离相似度】\n原理: 计算将一个文本转换为另一个所需的最少编辑操作次数\n特点: 关注字符级别的形式相似度\n适用: 拼写检查、短文本匹配","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":74,"column":1}},"key":"zVUaC5K0Fi"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":76,"column":1},"end":{"line":76,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“启发器”：把人类启发其他人类的能力交给AI，让AI启发我，形成循环。","position":{"start":{"line":76,"column":1},"end":{"line":76,"column":1}},"key":"WHEUG7JHZj"}],"key":"EtChqs6yd0"},{"type":"code","lang":"","value":"新知识发现\n▶ 发现1：“制度自反性”是创业组织抗脆弱性的核心算法\n\narticle9提出“审计审计自身”，article10将审计锚定于“可观测性”，article4的“立宪”本质是“对权力分配规则的持续重写”，article5的“权责契约”隐含对契约有效性的动态检验。四者共同指向：健康组织不追求静态完美制度，而构建能自我诊断、自我修复、自我迭代的元制度能力。这是区别于传统“制度建设”与“流程优化”的根本跃迁——制度本身成为第一学习对象。\n▶ 发现2：“利他式商业化”的真正护城河不在服务，而在“可验证的利他过程”\n\narticle1强调“故事即原型”，article2设计“调研式推销”，article9要求“审计真实反馈而非问卷形式”，article10直指“信息缺失即黑幕”。四者拼出完整图景：用户信任不来自承诺（“我们利他”），而来自可追溯、可审计、可参与的过程证据链（你参与的调研如何影响课程迭代？你的反馈是否进入周会议题？）。这使“利他”从价值观声明升维为可验证的产品特性。\n▶ 发现3：“竞赛模式”是贯穿技术、管理、市场的统一认知操作系统\n\narticle7的“竞赛模式”（得分制/开放/容错）在各文中均有回响：\n\n   article8中“RAG是大型上下文工程” ≈ 多刷题多存题 → 竞赛式知识储备\n   article4中“特种兵训练突破认知边界” ≈ 主线+副本任务 → 竞赛式能力成长\n   article2中“快速多轮调研试错” ≈ 快速迭代降低单次失败成本 → 竞赛式市场验证\n   article10中“接受流程断裂，先暴露再修复” ≈ 允许阶段性0分 → 竞赛式系统演进\n   → “竞赛模式”是该组织隐性但统一的方法论OS，比任何具体工具更具迁移价值。\n\n▶ 发现4：AI在此生态中扮演三重不可替代角色\n\n   认知脚手架（article1/2）：加速团队从“执行者”到“判断者”的跃迁；\n   情绪代偿物（article3）：替代耗竭性人际互动，提供无条件理解；\n   制度执行体（article8/9/10）：作为审计数据源、规则解析器、流程自动化载体。\n   → AI不是工具，而是组织神经系统的延伸，其价值在“人机协同制度化”中最大化。","position":{"start":{"line":78,"column":1},"end":{"line":102,"column":1}},"key":"tXgT548pCz"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"复盘","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"key":"oAmtnLamt5"}],"identifier":"id","label":"复盘","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"zM7yKpNt63"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":106,"column":1},"end":{"line":109,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"设计不受任何形式约束，只要有设计结果就可以了。\n设计结果具备意义是人赋予的。\n把模糊抽象的想法变成文档。\n幻觉甚至都可能可以被利用，只要可以被验证。","position":{"start":{"line":106,"column":1},"end":{"line":106,"column":1}},"key":"AOWA9BsbFU"}],"key":"Q4eauAAgQp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":112,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“发现而非发明”。\n分清主次","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":111,"column":1}},"key":"duCuaI3JQM"}],"key":"m5UubaDimH"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":114,"column":1},"end":{"line":117,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"需求赋予意义\n探索性学习\n项目导向学习\n好奇心是最好的老师","position":{"start":{"line":114,"column":1},"end":{"line":114,"column":1}},"key":"KH8ccm8BfQ"}],"key":"FmTkYWvs9s"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":119,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“人在情境中”","position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":119,"column":1}},"key":"eqsWAtR5o7"}],"key":"EBXuyhkmaB"}],"key":"YLR4gfO9pK"}],"key":"nGrAoBIQ6h"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}